 immediate left onto junipero serra boulevard turn left at the second stoplight campus drive east continue around campus drive east and turn left when you reach serra street follow serra street to encina hall and the small parking area immediately in front parking and entering pesd there are parking meters in the front of encina hall pesd is on the fourth floor of the east wing please enter up the steps and take an immediate left through the fsi reception and offices past the double doors take the elevator to the fourth floor go right out of the elevator to the end of the hall on your left from where pesd's receptionist will direct you please note that parking is monitored monday friday 8 am 4 pm contact voice 650 724 1714 fax 650 724 1717 search search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages campus map printable map of the stanford campus 2.9 mb with parking areas indicated marguerite bus map the marguerite is stanford university's campus shuttle a printable map of the bus routes serving the stanford campus 700kb support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 1714 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
